The paper proposes a method for automatic model design using neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on designing neural network architectures for image classification and language modeling tasks, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories.
